snippet.title: Ingression - First Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as Rina, a thief living in the year 2442 in the corrupt Galactic Empire. Travel to the future to save the past from a tremendous time paradox. Fulfill your destiny of keeping time intact.

🎮Wishlist now on Steam: https://bit.ly/3Q2vUtk
